title: THIS WILL CHANGE YOUR LIFE OVERNIGHT || EP:151
description:
Hey Rehabbers, 
Listen. YOUR LIFE CAN CHANGE OVERNIGHT! I know that sounds insane right, but let me clear something up. Your life doesn't change overnight, but change happens overnight! Too confusing?!? lol....Let me explain... Deciding not to settle for less, that choice can be made overnight. Choosing to stop living random, that choice happen overnight. The choice to change can happen overnight, but the harvest of that change takes time. If you LOCK IN on the 5 things I discuss on this episode, your life will change! STRAIGHT UP
This episode will open your heart up to that fact!
